---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- Visual side -->
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Scout badge-style card -->
          <div class="bg-brand-dark rounded-3xl p-8 text-white shadow-2xl">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-brand-gold flex items-center justify-center text-brand-dark">
                <Icon name="scout" class="w-8 h-8" />
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-heading font-bold text-lg text-brand-lime">Scout Alumni</div>
                <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Est. in the cedar forests of Lebanon</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
              "We met as teenagers in scouts, fell in love with the mountains, and with each other. After our wedding, we knew we had to find a way to share what Lebanon's nature had given us — the community, the discipline, the wonder."
            </p>
            <div class="flex gap-3">
              <div class="flex-1 bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-3 text-center">
                <div class="text-brand-gold font-bold text-lg">10+</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-gray-400">Years scouting</div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1 bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-3 text-center">
                <div class="text-brand-gold font-bold text-lg">Certified</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-gray-400">Wilderness First Aid</div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex-1 bg-white/10 rounded-xl p-3 text-center">
                <div class="text-brand-gold font-bold text-lg">Active</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-gray-400">Ongoing training</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-3 -left-3 w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-brand-lime/20 -z-10"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text side -->
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
        <span class="inline-block text-xs font-bold text-brand-primary uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Our Story</span>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Born from Scouts, Built for Lebanon</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            LebVentures was founded by a couple whose love story began in the Lebanese scouts — two young adventurers who spent their youth learning to navigate mountains, read the weather, and find community in the wilderness.
          </p>
          <p>
            After their marriage, they channeled their shared passion into building something bigger: a platform that connects people to Lebanon's extraordinary outdoors while staying true to the values scouting gave them — preparedness, respect for nature, and community above all.
          </p>
          <p>
            Both founders remain active and continuously trained in wilderness skills, first aid, and sustainable tourism best practices. Every adventure they lead is backed by current certifications and a genuine love for what they do.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          {['Wilderness First Aid', 'Leave No Trace', 'Rope & Rappel', 'Navigation', 'Flora & Fauna ID'].map(tag => (
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold bg-brand-sky text-brand-primary px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-brand-primary/20">
              {tag}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
